children.subject: yes, thanks for asking, I've updated the note.

Hi Lily,

Is it too late to register for this event? If so, would this mean we are not able to participate in the ceremony :(?
it's not too late, but please register asap :)
What is the deadline for filling this out? If we graduate this spring, can we still walk next Spring?
Thank you everyone for their patience, we do not yet have tickets, but once we do, we'll announce it.

history.content:
Dear graduating seniors and graduates (including Fall 15, Sum 15, Sp 16, Sum 16, Fall 16):

 

If you would like to participate in the L&S CS Commencement on Friday, May 20, 2016 in Zellerbach Auditorium at 9am, please register here: 2016 L&S CS Commencement Registration by MARCH 1.  We will be using your answers in the survey to construct the commencement program so please be sure to check your answers carefully!
 
If you are wondering about where to order your Cap & Gown, Graduation Announcements, Thank You cards, or assorted other graduation sundries, please begin your search at: http://commencement.berkeley.edu/getting-ready.
You can also visit the Student Stores in-person: 
  1. Cal Student Store, 2495 Bancroft Way, 510.229.4703
  2. The Student Store, 2480 Bancroft Way, 510.845.1226
 
Tickets to the L&S Commencement will be available for pick-up in L&S CS Advising Office at 377/379 Soda Hall, and we'll send out an annoucement when they are available.  All attendees must have a ticket (not including participating graduates) to attend the commencement. Students are guaranteed up to 4 tickets

If you have any other questions please don't hesitate to let us know, and keep up the great work!
